        </article>
        <article class="benefits">
        <div class="container">
        <h3 class="heading">Benefits</h3>
        <p>After implementing eTouch's solutions, the client saw immediate benefits:</p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li><span class="fa fa-angle-right"></span><span>Migration of the web channel platform to open source technology eliminated product support costs</span></li>
