        </ul>
        <p>eTouch helped the client establish a Testing Center of Excellence (TCoE) to manage and govern testing tools and processes. The move toward a cohesive online marketing platform with integration of ecommerce and content management solutions was a phenomenal success in the US. This has been replicated in Australia, Canada, India, and the UK.</p>
